The paper focuses on test case generation, which is a software engineering topic (cs.SE). It also mentions the use of code coverage criteria (cs.PL) and the evaluation of the approach on open-source Java projects (cs.SY). The paper proposes a novel integration-level coverage criterion (CBC), which could fall under machine learning (cs.LG) or artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories.
